{"tid":686478,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB五節目硬銷Big Big Channel 遭通訊局罰30萬兼嚴重警告","createTime":"2018-06-01T09:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T16:59:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"416538e96733e36f940714830a661da3c2a47494","tid":686478,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180601/large/1527845150_93fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180601%2Flarge%2F1527845150_93fd.png&h=8f76655d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫電視於去年多個節目中硬銷自家製作的「大台網」」(Big Big Channel)流動應用程式，通訊局接獲37個投訴並裁定無綫違反守則，向無綫罰款30萬元。<br />\n<br />\n5個被投訴節目為去年6月、7月及10月在無綫翡翠台播放的《Big Big小明星 2017》、《原來Big Big Channel咁好玩》、《群星拱照 Big Big Channel》和《Big Big Channel失驚無神賀中秋》，以及在翡翠台及now寬頻電視即日重播的《東張西望》。節目中從主題音樂、場景、吉祥物服飾、道具以至藝人表演等，都明顯展示該程式的標誌或名稱，通訊局認為這些展示及提述應被視作廣告材料。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局指該流動應用程式是獨立於無綫的企業實體，有服務內容與該台節目無直接關連，但在被投訴的5個節目中，該應用程式均無被識別為贊助商。因此，通訊局認為無綫4個節目違反《電視節目守則》中「禁止間接宣傳」及「不得過分突出屬於商業性質的產品及服務等」的條文，裁定罰款30萬元。而第5個被投訴節目《Big Big Channel 失驚無神賀中秋》被發出嚴重警告，重播被投訴節目的now寬頻電視則被發出勸諭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180601/58265612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F58265612&d=Qe4kh0FQtnTlaK23Hw01o4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=22f890ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F58265612&h=d7db0b8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180601/58265612</a>"},{"pid":"910ef081f5b919e6fde2c675e2fa1477b9886816","tid":686478,"uid":15483,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"罰咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\